## Pack Preview UI

Before installing, show:

```text
Benchmark name
Version
Supported platforms
Scenario count
Rank count
Threshold count
Native categories
Universal category coverage
Official/community/custom source
Warnings
Errors
```

Example:

```text
Viscose Community Pack
Version: 2026.1
Platform: KovaaK's
Scenarios: 84
Ranks: 8
Thresholds: 672
Source: Community
Warnings: 5 scenarios have no threshold data
Status: Safe to install
```

If invalid:

```text
Cannot install pack
Reason: threshold references missing scenario "abc"
```

