## UI Settings Page

Add a Benchmark Packs section in Settings.

UI should include:

```text
Installed Packs
- Voltaic     Built-in     Enabled
- Viscose     Built-in/User Installed     Enabled
- My Pack     Custom       Disabled

Actions
- Import Pack
- Create Custom Pack
- Enable / Disable
- View Details
- Validate Again
- Remove User Pack
```

Built-in packs cannot be removed, only disabled.

User packs can be removed.

