## Storage

Recommended local structure:

```text
AimBrainData/
  benchmark-packs/
    installed/
      viscose-community/
        pack.json
        README.md
    disabled/
    cache/
```

Also store pack settings in SQLite:

```text
benchmark_pack_settings
```

Fields:
- pack_id
- version
- source
- installed_path
- enabled
- installed_at
- last_validated_at
- validation_status

---

## Database Table

Add table:

```sql
CREATE TABLE benchmark_pack_settings (
  pack_id TEXT PRIMARY KEY,
  version TEXT NOT NULL,
  source TEXT NOT NULL,
  installed_path TEXT,
  enabled INTEGER NOT NULL DEFAULT 1,
  installed_at TEXT NOT NULL,
  last_validated_at TEXT,
  validation_status TEXT NOT NULL
);
```

Source values:
- built_in
- user_installed
- custom_created

