## Engine Flow With Packs

The engine flow:

```text
Raw runs
↓
Active benchmark pack selected
↓
Scenario matching using pack scenarios + aliases
↓
If threshold exists:
    rank progress
Else:
    progress-only stats
↓
Universal category mapping
↓
Weakness detection
↓
Recommendation
↓
UI analysis object
```

---

## UI Must Stay Benchmark-Agnostic

Bad:

```ts
if (benchmarkId === "voltaic") {
  showVoltaicRank();
}
```

Good:

```ts
const analysis = analyzeRuns({ runs, benchmarkPack });
showAnalysis(analysis);
```

The analysis object should already contain:
- benchmarkName
- scenarioName
- currentRank
- nextRank
- progressToNextRank
- normalizedProgress
- hasThresholdData
- note
- category
- universalCategory
- recommendation

