## Success Criteria

This implementation is successful when:

- Codex can add a new benchmark by creating a pack folder and pack.json.
- A user can import a pack.json from the app.
- Invalid packs show clear errors.
- Valid packs appear in Settings.
- A pack can be enabled/disabled.
- The engine can analyze runs using the active pack.
- Missing thresholds return progress-only mode.
- UI does not need benchmark-specific if-statements.

