## External Source Adapter Update

Benchmark packs should not be Aim Brain-only.

A user should be able to get benchmark definitions from common sources, then Aim Brain normalizes them.

Supported source direction:

```text
Built-in curated packs
Local pack.json
Local CSV
GitHub raw JSON/CSV
Public Google Sheet CSV
.aimbrainpack later
Custom builder later
```

